00:45:45.328 --> 00:45:48.580
Remember when you came
to Hilton Head with us in second grade

772
00:45:49.414 --> 00:45:52.042
and you cried the whole flight?

773
00:45:52.542 --> 00:45:54.586
<i>Sit back. enjoy the flight.</i>

774
00:45:55.254 --> 00:45:56.254
Here.

775
00:45:57.422 --> 00:45:59.716
Swiped these
from my mom's medicine cabinet.

776
00:45:59.800 --> 00:46:00.800
Valium.

777
00:46:01.426 --> 00:46:03.804
She's got.
like. a never-ending supply.

778
00:46:03.887 --> 00:46:05.514
so I doubt she'll even notice.

779
00:46:07.140 --> 00:46:08.140
I know.

780
00:46:08.433 --> 00:46:09.851
I'm basically the best.

781
00:46:12.271 --> 00:46:13.271
And here.

782
00:46:14.439 --> 00:46:15.649
It's a good luck charm.

783
00:46:19.778 --> 00:46:21.154
Now nothing can touch you.

784
00:47:06.450 --> 00:47:07.450
Sorry I'm late.

785
00:47:10.871 --> 00:47:12.789
A reporter approached me today.

786
00:47:14.791 --> 00:47:16.269
She said she was with the local paper.

787
00:47:16.293 --> 00:47:18.086
but I googled her.

788
00:47:18.170 --> 00:47:21.214
and she wasn't credited
in any bylines anywhere.

789
00:47:23.633 --> 00:47:25.570
These people come out
of the woodwork every few years

790
00:47:25.594 --> 00:47:26.928
on some anniversary or another.

791
00:47:27.012 --> 00:47:28.012
You know that.

792
00:47:28.555 --> 00:47:30.475
There's no reason to think
this is any different.

793
00:47:30.807 --> 00:47:32.225
I can think of a few.

794
00:47:33.393 --> 00:47:34.393
We agreed.

795
00:47:35.145 --> 00:47:36.396
Say no more than we have to.

796
00:47:36.730 --> 00:47:38.857
stay out of the public eye.

797
00:47:38.940 --> 00:47:39.940
Shauna.

798
00:47:39.983 --> 00:47:42.903
I saw you on fucking television. Ty.

799
00:47:43.737 --> 00:47:44.905
If someone's digging.

800
00:47:45.614 --> 00:47:47.032
we are all fucked.

801
00:47:47.699 --> 00:47:48.909
Take care of it.

802
00:47:52.537 --> 00:47:53.537
Thank you.

803
00:47:59.628 --> 00:48:00.837
Have you talked to Nat?

804
00:48:02.172 --> 00:48:04.216
She's in rehab. Again.

805
00:48:06.385 --> 00:48:08.553
And there's still no sign of the others?

806
00:48:08.637 --> 00:48:09.638
No.

807
00:48:09.721 --> 00:48:10.721
Not for months.

808
00:48:13.225 --> 00:48:14.225
Okay.

809
00:48:16.061 --> 00:48:17.061
Then we're fine.

810
00:48:24.778 --> 00:48:27.072
So long as nobody does anything crazy...

811
00:48:29.074 --> 00:48:30.575
we have nothing to worry about.

812
00:49:12.033 --> 00:49:13.076
Nice ride.

813
00:49:18.165 --> 00:49:20.375
I'm Dave. The manager.

814
00:49:21.418 --> 00:49:22.419
Hi. Dave.

815
00:49:25.422 --> 00:49:26.798
I'm sorry. It's just...

816
00:49:27.299 --> 00:49:30.093
Haven't seen anyone around this unit
since I've been here.

817
00:49:31.261 --> 00:49:33.346
Vultures have been circling it for years.

818
00:49:33.430 --> 00:49:34.598
but I keep telling 'em.

819
00:49:34.681 --> 00:49:36.892
"Long as the bill's paid."

820
00:49:39.019 --> 00:49:40.228
You local?

821
00:49:41.188 --> 00:49:42.188
Was.

822
00:49:43.148 --> 00:49:45.025
Been a while since I've been...

823
00:49:45.525 --> 00:49:46.525
home.

824
00:49:47.402 --> 00:49:48.842
Then welcome back.

825
00:49:49.196 --> 00:49:50.196
Thanks.

826
00:49:51.823 --> 00:49:54.075
I wasn't sure how I'd feel. but...

827
00:49:54.993 --> 00:49:56.536
I think it'll be good to...

828
00:49:57.245 --> 00:50:00.207
reconnect with some old friends.

829
00:50:54.719 --> 00:50:56.555
Happy Friday. Mrs. DeGenaro.

830
00:50:58.890 --> 00:51:00.517
Time for your meds.

831
00:51:01.935 --> 00:51:03.311
We been a good girl today?

832
00:51:07.649 --> 00:51:08.649
Mm.

833
00:51:09.109 --> 00:51:10.777
Still on a hunger strike. I see.

834
00:51:12.070 --> 00:51:14.656
You know. you're never gonna get
your strength back up

835
00:51:14.739 --> 00:51:15.739
if you don't eat.

836
00:51:18.618 --> 00:51:19.618
Gloria.

837
00:51:20.870 --> 00:51:22.330
Did we have another accident?

838
00:51:25.083 --> 00:51:27.752
I have told you.
you just have to press the button

839
00:51:27.836 --> 00:51:29.421
and someone will come.

840
00:51:31.715 --> 00:51:33.235
I just changed those sheets.

841
00:51:49.065 --> 00:51:50.065
You know...

842
00:51:51.776 --> 00:51:55.071
I think the morphine
might be upsetting your tummy.

843
00:52:00.619 --> 00:52:02.287
Let's skip this dose.

844
00:52:04.706 --> 00:52:06.124
Mm-mm.

845
00:52:06.458 --> 00:52:07.626
Don't fuck with me.

846
00:52:17.218 --> 00:52:18.720
Happy Friday. ladies!

847
00:52:19.554 --> 00:52:20.472
Hey. Misty.

848
00:54:24.596 --> 00:54:25.596
The Lord is my shepherd.

849
00:54:26.598 --> 00:54:27.867
And even though I walk
through the valley...
